## Origin Note

This dual-licensing structure reflects the origin of GET: a theoretical framework that emerged during the creation of a fictional universe. The theory is shared openly for scientific discourse; the story remains protected IP.

*The theory is real. The universe it helped create is fiction. Both belong to the same journey.*

